com.github.mrgoro.interactivedata.api.data.operations

Class EmptyOperationData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.mrgoro.interactivedata.api.data.operations.EmptyOperationData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OperationData, java.io.Serializable

    public class EmptyOperationData
extends java.lang.Object
implements OperationData
    Placeholder class specifying that the Operation does not need to be parameterized.

    Note: The hasData() method always return true as there is no possibility to derive this information from zero data. Therefore the Operations always operates - which should always be the case.

    Author:
    Philipp Schürmann
